Marvin Stephens https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marvin_Stephens 0 Marvin Stephens (born 1923) is a retired American film actor. A child actor, his first Hollywood roles were in the Mickey McGuire films. Stephens then played the recurring role of Tommy McGuire in Twentieth Century Fox's Jones Family series of films.
